Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.68,0:01:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.29,0:01:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不去上學 就在這懶懶散散無所事事渾渾噩噩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死啦！我自己能收拾 你出去啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啦是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.17,0:02:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波說今晚要開個誓師大會 你怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也搞不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣 總之先在車站前面等…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了 鶴見你是根本沒吃夠苦頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副「只有自己才瞭解松雪同學」的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高181厘米 體重68公斤 喜歡吃的東西是八橋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:58.15,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八橋（八ツ橋）：京都代表性的名點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛好是女裝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女裝?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！鶴見 話還沒說完…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想把那事傳得盡人皆知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.78,0:03:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來來 動起手來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是為芽間明天成佛而設的大宴會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好地裝點一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間用紙巾來做花～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你可是宴會的主角啊 為什麼還自己動手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很好玩嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！芽間很行嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 別發呆了 快用傳單做垃圾箱 垃圾箱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾箱？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:04:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前啊 我在班上不是很沒用嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能靠做傻事引人注意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.40,0:04:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 仁碳你們卻讓我成為了大家的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然…到頭來…也只能看著大家而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能看著…而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這次啊 全部都讓我一個人操辦好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會氣氣派派地送你走的哦 芽間！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託您了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.04,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}波波真是體貼呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個事情 打算怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能…去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把人愚弄到什麼地步他們才滿意？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群小孩 到底要到什麼地步…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊 小聰？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！冷靜點！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老媽啊 你知道我身高多少嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一年來 我可是長高了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都很孤單吧 你 還有聰志
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能忘記掉芽衣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也沒關係 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起分擔孤單吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 和聰志 還有我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人一起分擔…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變成什麼樣子呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說 如果把煙花放上去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說如果芽間不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我也想過好多次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得如果芽間不在了 跟仁碳最要好的就會是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當芽間真的不在了 跟仁碳的距離卻拉得遠遠的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然 距離又開始縮短了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這也是因為芽間回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天去秘密基地嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟安城在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…？嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孬種
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鶴見子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你那麼信誓旦旦地說要讓她成佛 到了關鍵時刻又怕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒出息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為害怕 所以逃離了芽間而跟安城在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是希望悲慘的不僅僅是你自己吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:06:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.99,0:07:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間在電話裡叫我們出來的時候 她說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說「為了仁碳 我有事情想拜託你們」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 雪集？鶴見子說了什…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這是只有你才能做的事情 安鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群傢伙 為啥不來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:33.18,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(646,120)}{\c&H3842BB&}再{\c&H538BEC&}見{\c&H4FFFF0&}了 {\c&H51B25B&}芽{\c&HA07E37&}間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦 反正明天也會見面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫他們！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？喂 波波！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見子！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去買了些點心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦！不愧是鶴見子！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:52.62,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}哦哦！愛死你了 雪集！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！開party啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:57.12,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Party party…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信的！我真的是相信你們的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開心死我了 真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！我愛死這個了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:02.48,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}居然到齊了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.99,0:08:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺…一切就要迎來結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 芽間和我們 組成了「超和平Busters」…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開場白就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.95,0:08:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 請主角芽間 上前來！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～！
