Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:41.83,writings4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(947,158)}也想跟大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:41.83,writings4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(364,316)}繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:41.83,writings4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(945,340)}做好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:41.83,writings4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(413,496)\c&H81AC7F&}請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝芽間的致辭！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間 吃這個不？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅通通的 辣的東西吃起來喉嚨疼 不幹！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…「辣的」…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:02.30,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}沒這種事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:05.74,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}沒問題的 吃一口試試啦 張嘴啦 芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.74,0:09:06.95,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}嘴巴好辣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼餘興節目麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不就變成吃喝大會了麼 這是誓師大會吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會難得 來搞點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.87,0:09:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餘興節目…要搞什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再搞一次 那一天的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.99,0:09:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 在這裡發生的事情 重現一次如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說「在這裡發生的事情」…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑！做這種事有什麼意義…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…仁碳你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡芽間…吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:10:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間也在這裡吧？給我清楚地說出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說啊…說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說啊 說啊 說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:19.45,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}說啊 說啊 說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！這也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用做得這麼過分吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:33.18,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}說啊 說啊 說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…對芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.98,0:10:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑的話 一切就跟那時一樣了！仁碳！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間什麼都沒說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼淚叭嗒叭嗒地往下掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:04.02,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(579,199)}第十集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:04.02,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(566,393)}煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也該哭夠了吧 很難看的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我就是難看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是雪集的主意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我說啊 還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 那天的回答 大家不是都明白的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算芽間成佛了 仍然搞得不清不楚 滿腹疑惑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.62,0:11:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直輸給本已不存在的芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你也能接受嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見子你不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己喜歡的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠都不回頭看你一眼這種感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我喜歡雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集他一直在追尋著芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個身影 我一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道什麼是永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果芽間成佛了 宿海就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 雪集他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會選擇我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為就算芽間成佛了 替代她的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會是安城你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！說什麼替代 雪集他從來沒想過這種事情！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 就算我再怎麼痛苦 也不會跟雪集在一起的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我就是喜歡仁碳啊…根本沒人可以取代他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 就是因為沒有可以取代的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 必須…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓芽間成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 仁碳 剛才跟著起哄了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得 一切都像回到了從前一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到從前…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.22,0:13:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是真心的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是真…的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間也喜歡仁碳～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖 雖說是喜歡…不過不只是朋友間的那種喜歡啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的啊 是想讓我嫁給你的那種喜歡吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間我啊 要是也能普普通通地像這樣長大的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會不會 成為仁碳的妻子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不是…普通地…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不成佛 像現在這樣留下來不也挺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:13:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…出來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.56,0:14:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會成佛的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為啊 我會轉世的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不成佛的話 就沒辦法轉世了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能跟大家一起好好地聊天了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:26.99,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}但是 如果變成了青蟲的話怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「跟大家…好好地…」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳說喜歡你了 你會怎麼回答呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說「為了仁碳 我有事情想拜託你們」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道答案的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…對芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就是明擺著的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 已經無所謂了…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.31,0:15:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成佛吧 好吧？芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一個人的話…不行嗎 芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 小芽間 你知道「轉世」是什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.53,0:15:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉世？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這一生結束了 還會變成小嬰兒 再回到這個世上活下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 也可能不是作為人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是作為小貓的孩子 花兒的孩子之類的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊 一點都不會孤單的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:16:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊 只有一件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨 再給我點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要為我放煙花 所以 再給我點時間…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 先把附加物安裝好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:36.53,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}註：附加物（ショイモノ） 是指龍勢煙花上附加的東西 可以有降落傘 小煙花和旗子等各種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:16:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好可愛！鶴見子像小時候一樣～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是搞啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想轉換心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 拿著那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二三！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.53,0:17:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 好像聞到了很熟悉的味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是仁碳你叫小聰來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你…仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:17:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…要結束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.15,0:18:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二三！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 芽間跟我們的目的已經一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對會讓你成佛的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的話 還能夠阻止…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.65,0:18:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間她 一定會很高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會讓你阻止的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.04,0:18:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的話 還能夠阻止…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能阻止的 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會成佛的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～小聰好有力氣！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 剩下的就是放上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我說啊 還有什麼想說的東西不…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她弟弟在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就衝著天說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊——好開心啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許許多多事情 謝謝你了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁碳也來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.69,0:19:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要開始了 要是弄太晚了會打擾到附近的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎…現在的話 還能阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能阻止…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙花…放上去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～！花兒在天空綻放了～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽…間…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還在？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！她還在啊?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.03,0:21:20.76,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}喂 我說 仁碳！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.81,0:21:22.22,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}哎？怎麼了怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那個時候 我心裡想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「你沒有消失 太好了」…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
